          <msContents>
            <summary><p>1 fol. on parchment; Sold 27 Apr 2017 as Lot 19; Qurʾānic Text: Q 2:282-2:286; 15 lines per page; Dimensions: 357 x 276mm; Script style: kūfī D; Estimated date of production: 800-1000. </p><p> </p><p>For a detailed catalogue entry about the Blue Qurʾān, including a large  list of sister fragments scattered in collections around the world, see  entry <ref target="https://corpuscoranicum.de/handschriften/index/sure/2/vers/286?handschrift=1458">HC.MS.03223</ref> (written by Marcus Fraser). Some of the metadata was carried over from that manuscript.</p><p> </p>Further information can also be found on <ref target="https://www.christies.com/en/lot/lot-6065364?ldp_breadcrumb=back">Christie's website</ref>.<p/></summary>
